column2: TINDAKMALAYSIA NETWORK SERVICES PLT (TINDAK MALAYSIA)
Election Commission of Malaysia (SPR), Tindak Malaysia (2023), Attorney General Chambers, Malaysiakini (https://www.malaysiakini.com/news/684332)

This is the non-gazetted official results from SPR. A selected number of values for Sekolah Kebangsaan Jepak are missing as SPR FB live did not show remaining values of 5 salurans. All early voters became postal voters.  TindakMalaysia Network Services PLT is not responsible for any errors or ommissions arising from the original data or its derivatives
